content: I'm excited to start using these features to organize my Disney World trip entry. I think I'll add tags like #DisneyWorld, #MagicKingdom, and #RollerCoasters to help me quickly find related entries. And, I'll use the map feature to mark the different parks and attractions we visited, like the Seven Dwarfs Mine Train rollercoaster. This will really help me relive the trip and plan future adventures. What's next? Can you show me how to use the photo and audio features in Day One?
